<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
<title>Avaliar seu negocio | 1Negocio</title>
<script async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-7DGLH0W7KE"></script>
<script>window.dataLayer=window.dataLayer||[];function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments)}gtag('js',new Date());gtag('config','G-7DGLH0W7KE');</script>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@400;600;700;800&family=DM+Mono:wght@300;400;500&family=Cabinet+Grotesk:wght@400;500;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{--bg:#080d0a;--bg1:#0e1510;--em:#3dff7a;--am:#ffb03a;--ink:#f0f5f1;--ink2:#a8b8ac;--ink3:#5a7060;--line:rgba(255,255,255,.08);--r:10px}
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
body{min-height:100vh;background:var(--bg);color:var(--ink);font-family:'Cabinet Grotesk',sans-serif;padding-bottom:100px}
.container{max-width:480px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 16px}
.header{padding:16px 0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between}
.logo{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:15px;text-decoration:none;color:var(--ink)}
.logo em{color:var(--em);font-style:normal}
.back{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--ink3);text-decoration:none}
.hero{text-align:center;padding:32px 0 24px}
.hero h1{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:24px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:12px}
.hero h1 .em{color:var(--em)}
.hero p{font-size:13px;color:var(--ink2);line-height:1.6}
.section{margin-bottom:20px}
.section-label{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:8px;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--em);margin-bottom:10px}
.box{background:var(--bg1);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:var(--r);padding:16px}
.item{padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}
.item:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.item h3{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:4px}
.item p{font-size:11px;color:var(--ink3);line-height:1.5}
.grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:8px;margin-bottom:16px}
.stat{background:var(--bg1);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:var(--r);padding:12px;text-align:center}
.stat-value{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:18px;color:var(--em)}
.stat-label{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:8px;color:var(--ink3);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;margin-top:4px}
.cta-fixed{position:fixed;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;background:linear-gradient(to top,var(--bg) 70%,transparent);padding:12px 16px 24px}
.cta-inner{max-width:480px;margin:0 auto}
.btn{width:100%;background:var(--em);color:#080d0a;border:none;border-radius:var(--r);padding:14px;font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;cursor:pointer;text-decoration:none;display:block;text-align:center}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
  <header class="header">
    <a href="index.html" class="logo"><em>1</em>Negocio</a>
    <a href="index.html" class="back">Voltar</a>
  </header>
  
  <div class="hero">
    <h1>QUANTO VALE O SEU <span class="em">NEGOCIO</span>?</h1>
    <p>Descubra em 5-10 minutos com a avaliacao gratuita da 1Negocio.</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="grid">
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat-value">5-10</div>
      <div class="stat-label">minutos</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat-value">10+30</div>
      <div class="stat-label">perguntas</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-label">O que voce recebe</div>
    <div class="box">
      <div class="item">
        <h3>Valor do negocio</h3>
        <p>Avaliacao tecnica baseada em fluxo de caixa, multiplo setorial e maturidade empresarial.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="item">
        <h3>DRE ajustado</h3>
        <p>Demonstrativo de resultado reconstruido com base nos dados declarados.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="item">
        <h3>Indice de Solidez (ISE)</h3>
        <p>Nota de 0 a 100 medindo a saude operacional do seu negocio em 10 dimensoes.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="item">
        <h3>Benchmark setorial</h3>
        <p>Compare sua margem, crescimento e eficiencia com a media do seu setor.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="item">
        <h3>Acoes de melhoria</h3>
        <p>Sugestoes quantificadas para aumentar o valor do negocio.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-label">Metodologia</div>
    <div class="box">
      <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--ink2);line-height:1.6">
        Avaliacao baseada em Resultado Operacional x Fator 1N. 
        O Fator 1N combina multiplo de mercado, maturidade empresarial (ISE) 
        e confiabilidade dos dados (ICD). 
        Metodologia propria desenvolvida para PMEs brasileiras.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<div class="cta-fixed">
  <div class="cta-inner">
    <a href="1avaliacao.html" class="btn">Iniciar avaliacao gratuita</a>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
